##Do not travel to the United States, the Ministry of Culture and Tourism Warns

The papernews

The function introduction, has the connotation the current politics new media

Zheng Haiou / People's Daily client

People's Daily client February 24 news, the reporter learned from the Ministry of Culture and Tourism: the Ministry of Culture and tourism issued a travel safety alert to the United States. Recently, due to the excessive anti-epidemic measures of the United States and the security situation in the United States, Chinese tourists have been treated unfairly in the United States. The Ministry of Culture and tourism has warned Chinese tourists to be more aware of safety precautions and not to travel to the United States.

This issue is edited by Chang Chen
